      "title": "No train strike tonight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Railways Station Masters' Union (SLRSMU) has decided to cancel the scheduled train strike tonight, following decisions taken by the Railways General Manager.",
        "The decision to launch a 24-hour strike starting from midnight today was by the railway trade union due to the unavailability of fuel for them to report for duty.",
        "Following the termination of services, at least 180 train services had to be suspended today. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
